General.Name: Magnum Mining and Exploration Ltd
General.Description: Magnum Mining and Exploration Limited engages in the exploration and evaluation of mineral properties. The company owns a 74% interest in the Gravelotte emerald project located in the Limpopo province of South Africa. It has an agreement to acquire a 100% interest in the Buena Vista iron ore project located in Nevada, United States. Magnum Mining and Exploration Limited was incorporated in 1986 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
